{"tid":610584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港交所：12]黃錦星：係咪一定要（保育）南生圍","createTime":"2018-03-30T05:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T20:26:24.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff9b289036800f381d02d76cf255633b21d5472","tid":610584,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180329/s00002/1522260103437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180329%2Fs00002%2F1522260103437&d=DE904%2F16tISvZ0qSGm9fkAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=55459cdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180329%2Fs00002%2F1522260103437&h=e72e6eef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180329/s00002/1522260103437</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】本月中南生圍接連兩日發生火警，消防處懷疑起火成因有可疑，環境局長黃錦星昨於立法會接受議員質詢時表示，消防處已將兩宗山火一併交警方調查。多名議員促政府動用公帑回購南生圍私人土地，惟黃錦星認為涉及龐大資源，要考慮優先次序，反問「係咪一定要（保育）南生圍」。<br />\n<br />\n指火災未顯著影響生態<br />\n<br />\n黃錦星表示，火警後，漁護署立即到南生圍當地視察，發現受山火影響地方包括塘壆草被及蘆葦叢，幸火災後仍觀察到多種雀鳥，包括黑臉琵鷺、鷺鶿及棲息於蘆葦叢的雀鳥仍然在南生圍覓食或棲息，暫時未見火災對南生圍生態造成顯著或長遠的不良影響。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟范國威指南生圍在過去11年發生7宗山火，火警後較容易通過城規會申請。議會陣線朱凱廸認為，政府應動用公帑收回南生圍私人土地保育。<br />\n<br />\n黃錦星回應指不應將山火與城規會申請混為一談。至於應否回購私人土地保育，黃強調涉及龐大資源，應考慮保育的優先次序，現時全港有12個高生態價值地點，<span style=\"color: red;\">以米埔居首，南生圍排第9，反問「係咪一定要（保育）南生圍呢」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f54b7efc6308028afdab01263dffbe3b8a46cc8","tid":610584,"uid":26752,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:49:08.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fab30b471b8352a6a5e72a8f2f93e03774010b8","tid":610584,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"香港唔需要保育<br />\n無價值<br />\n起樓就夠"},{"pid":"8116dbee0fb20e27746c29425cba5e4b596fb395","tid":610584,"uid":60545,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"咁幾時拆咗政總去起公屋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5f179507f3f846c4abed30e1f3fd680047c676","tid":610584,"uid":168171,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T05:55:50.000Z","msg":"保咩育！用嚟起樓啦"},{"pid":"882eb1009d8a00d9f87270b6df185694c4c153ea","tid":610584,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:10:29.000Z","msg":"問到價<br />\n南生豪庭駛唔駛3萬蚊呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc66c92d296f904ad5582a1bfca14875a909696","tid":610584,"uid":41818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:12:02.000Z","msg":"排第9就代表唔駛保育？<br />\n咩logic"},{"pid":"265dfc67af64d12c58cbd31c213d7f3da523250f","tid":610584,"uid":13503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:14:03.000Z","msg":"之後排第8、7、6、5、4 洗唔洗保育"},{"pid":"9c1d7b0fec6fb45178edd2735b3baa1da450f8b7","tid":610584,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc09aa298b5ba58e470c0eb077ab4ce13d0e6383","tid":610584,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c1d7b0fec6fb45178edd2735b3baa1da450f8b7","tid":610584,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /